data — what we collect, what we don&#x27;t, and what we do with the little we have.\"/><meta property=\"og:site_name\" content=\"OpenGolfAPI\"/><meta property=\"og:type\" content=\"website\"/><meta name=\"twitter:card\" content=\"summary\"/><meta name=\"twitter:title\" content=\"OpenGolfAPI — The Open Golf Course Database\"/><meta name=\"twitter:description\" content=\"How OpenGolfAPI handles your data — what we collect, what we don&#x27;t, and what we do with the little we have.\"/><link rel=\"icon\" href=\"/favicon.ico?favicon.0x3dzn~oxb6tn.ico\" sizes=\"256x256\" type=\"image/x-icon\"/><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/03~yq9q893hmn.js\" noModule=\"\"></script></head><body class=\"min-h-full flex flex-col\"><div hidden=\"\"><!--$--><!--/$--></div><header class=\"bg-cream border-b border-cream-darkest\" style=\"background:var(--color-cream);border-color:var(--color-cream-darkest)\"><nav class=\"max-w-[1100px] mx-auto px-6 h-16 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"font-display text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight\" style=\"color:var(--color-evergreen-950)\" href=\"/\">Open<em style=\"color:var(--color-brass-700);font-style:italic\">Golf</em>API</a><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-sm\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink-muted)\"><details class=\"relative group [&amp;[open]&gt;summary&gt;span]:rotate-180\"><summary class=\"list-none cursor-pointer hover:text-[var(--color-evergreen-950)] transition-colors inline-flex items-center gap-1 select-none\">Browse<span class=\"text-[10px] transition-transform duration-150\" aria-hidden=\"true\">▾</span></summary><div class=\"absolute right-0 top-full mt-2 z-50\"><div class=\"grid grid-cols-5 gap-1 p-3 bg-white rounded-md shadow-xl border\" style=\"border-color:var(--color-cream-darkest)\"><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-ink)\" href=\"/courses/al\">AL</a><a class=\"px-2 py-1 text-xs rounded hover:bg-[var(--color-cream)]\" style=\"color:var(--color-in